import React from 'react';
import ProjectHeader from '../components/ProjectHeader';

import ProjectPic from '../components/ProjectPic';


const Tottot = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <ProjectHeader project="tottot - question game" text="Ett kul frågespel! DDsikutera med bänner.
        Ett kul frågespel! DDsikutera med bänner.Ett kul frågespel! DDsikutera med bänner.

But really, another social media platform? Irrelevant posts? Algorithms creating information bubbles? Cyber bullying? Selling user data?
We say no. It’s time for something new. It’s time for users to be in control. It ́s about time gamers get their own social network and connect with integrity.
Welcome to the Good Gaming Community. Let’s Sweep!"></ProjectDesc>

            <ProjectDesc desc="the process" text="what the heck did you do"></ProjectDesc>

                text="Question game for you and your friends."></ProjectHeader>
            <ProjectPic src="./tottotiphone.png"></ProjectPic>
            <ProjectDesc
                desc="goal for the project"
                text="I was asked from the client to design a User Interface for the platform.The client presented me with
            somewhat of a wireframe and a specification of the functionalities to be included. "></ProjectDesc>
            <ProjectDesc
                desc="the process"
                text=""></ProjectDesc>
            <ProjectPic src="./tfniphone.png"></ProjectPic>
            <ProjectDesc
                desc="the outcome"
                text="..."></ProjectDesc>


        </>

export default Tottot;
